<view class="page">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-kicker">Memory Wall</view>
    <view class="hero-title">回忆墙</view>
    <view class="hero-copy">
      把你们一起吃过、玩过、拍过、完成过的事，慢慢沉淀成能反复回看的生活。
    </view>
    <view class="hero-row">
      <view class="hero-pill" wx:if="{{relation}}">{{relation.partner.name || 'TA'}} 的共同回忆</view>
      <view class="hero-pill">{{memories.length}} 条正在展示</view>
      <view class="hero-link" bindtap="goToChat">动作消息</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view scroll-x class="filter-scroll" show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
    <view class="filter-row">
      <view
        wx:for="{{filters}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="filter-chip {{selectedModule === item.id ? 'filter-chip-active' : ''}}"
        data-module="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="selectFilter"
      >
        {{item.label}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="empty-card" wx:if="{{!loading && !memories.length}}">
    <view class="empty-title">还没有记录落到回忆墙里</view>
    <view class="empty-copy">
      去吃、去玩、去拍，或者发起一个小任务，完成后这里就会慢慢长出有温度的时间线。
    </view>
    <view class="empty-actions">
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="goToLove">回关系页</button>
      <button class="warm-button" bindtap="goToDiscover">去发现灵感</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="memory-list" wx:else>
    <view class="memory-card" wx:for="{{memories}}" wx:key="_id">
      <view class="memory-head">
        <view class="memory-meta">
          <view class="memory-module">{{item.moduleLabel}}</view>
          <view class="memory-time">{{item.createdAtText}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="memory-tag">{{item.templateLabel}}</view>
      </view>

      <view class="memory-title">{{item.title}}</view>
      <view class="memory-summary">{{item.summary || item.content}}</view>
      <view class="memory-participants" wx:if="{{item.participantsText}}">
        {{item.participantsText}}
      </view>

      <image
        wx:if="{{item.coverImage}}"
        class="memory-cover"
        src="{{item.coverImage}}"
        mode="aspectFill"
        data-images="{{item.mediaList}}"
        data-current="{{item.coverImage}}"
        bindtap="previewMemoryMedia"
      />
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="load-more" wx:if="{{hasMore}}" bindtap="loadMore">
    <text>{{loadingMore ? '正在加载更多回忆...' : '加载更多回忆'}}</text>
  </view>
</view>
